<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Teste - Proposta Comercial</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --blue: #0047ba;
            --text: #2e2e2e;
            --text-muted: #374151;
            --gray: #6B7280;
            --border: #E5E7EB;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: #D1D5DB;
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        .document {
            max-width: 210mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 24px 0;
        }

        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            background: #fcfcfc;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
            padding: 46px 56px 120px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        .page::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('fundo-center.png') center center no-repeat;
            background-size: 602px auto;
            opacity: 0.03;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .logo {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--blue);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            padding: 24px 56px 32px;
            z-index: 10;
            background: rgba(252, 252, 252, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
        }
        .footer-line {
            height: 2px;
            background: #e5e7eb80;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .footer-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .footer-logo {
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .footer-logo img {
            width: 74px;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }
        .pg-num {
            font-size: 12.5px;
            color: var(--blue);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="document">
    <div class="page">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="logo-wa-project.png" alt="Wa Project">
            </div>

            <h1>Teste do Template</h1>
            <p>Este é um teste para verificar se as imagens e footer estão funcionando.</p>
            <p>Logo deve aparecer acima e footer deve aparecer embaixo com logo menor.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-line"></div>
            <div class="footer-row">
                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <img src="logo-wa-project.png" alt="Wa Project">
                </div>
                <span class="pg-num">Teste</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>